title: My Sect's Senior Disciple Has A Hole In His Brain

status: There's a Pit in My Senior's Brain ; There's Something Wrong with My Da Shixiong's Brain ; Wo Jia Da Shi Xiong Nao Zi You Keng ; 我家大师兄脑子有坑
description:
Description :
        The hilarious adventures of the eldest disciple of a sect who has a problem with his brain. Dong Fang Xian Yun was reincarnated as the most senior disciple of the Carefree sect. But the only thing that goes through his mind is to make sure he doesn't end up dying by the hands of the "main character". Read as he makes no sense to his fellow disciples while avoiding flags left and right.    *Note : Although there are many chapters listed as missing, nothing is actually missing, some of chapter combining into one.*
